{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Introduce a new tax code for emergency workers and armed forces",
        "additional_details": "We believe that workers in the above sectors have already made sacrifices both personally and professionally in order to provide an unattainable level of public service anywhere else in the world. Many workers have and continue to spend a copious amount of time away from their own lives, friends and families as well as risking their own lives and wellness both mentally and physically in order to provide a service to the rest of society.",
        "background": "The Government should introduce a new tax code system for those working as emergency service workers, in the armed forces and in the public sector at a discounted rate.",
